  "commit_message": "Add regression tests for Issue #3849 (#5280)\n\nAdd tests to verify that Assert.Catch inside Assert.Multiple reports\nclear assertion failure messages instead of throwing InvalidCastException.\n\nThe bug was caused by explicit casting in Catch<TActual> returning\n(TActual?)Throws(...) which throws when the exception type doesn't match.\nThe fix (already in main) uses 'as TExpected' which returns null instead.\n\nThese tests ensure the fix remains in place.\n\nFixes #3849\n\nCo-authored-by: Claude Opus 4.5 <n",
